{"tid":520193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大公報連睇場波都可以上A1","createTime":"2018-01-05T07:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T07:34:53.000Z","uid":33890,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8786c82e5b9a5caaefceeaff9afee7f076dc4fd","tid":520193,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:16:46.000Z","msg":"係唔係真係無新聞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/151601_8698be001a5795096669d3106ea90d40.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F151601_8698be001a5795096669d3106ea90d40.jpg&h=58be5033&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0eb5389d5c9e708b8689f1aa7d094ce3224e7e08","tid":520193,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:23:45.000Z","msg":"// 昨日省港杯賽果，香港隊2：0先勝一場。惟「港獨」球迷賽後對廣東隊狂叫「返大陸」、「返大陸」的惡劣行徑，猶如一粒老鼠屎搞壞一煲湯，玷污了港隊值得自豪的勝利。 //<br />\n<br />\n成日覺得大公報唔俾人叫返大陸係「唆擺他人犯罪」<br />\n唔返大陸咪違反逗留條件囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過講真<br />\n雖然講粗口舉中指係省港杯傳統<br />\n但呢場波未至於要講哂粗口舉哂中指掛<br />\n因為廣東隊由頭到尾成隊收哂皮咁(除咗中柱嗰下)"},{"pid":"52b2788f2cd48352c77ac284503844757e720290","tid":520193,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"嚴厲打擊港獨狗是不需要手軟的"},{"pid":"00405cefec94160493b981468c11c044461040ae","tid":520193,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"太公報仲有人睇嘅咩？"},{"pid":"12ad0a2a6b09b273cc32953c56e03394d8cc3b6a","tid":520193,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://paper.takungpao.com/resfile/PDF/20180105/PDF/a1_screen.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.takungpao.com%2Fresfile%2FPDF%2F20180105%2FPDF%2Fa1_screen.pdf&d=RS8OccpzGdwe2pTUvewOpWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8eaa43c7\" target=\"_blank